      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/bitter-gourds-and-honey-for-the-soul\nPublished: 2024-07-17 --- Acts 17:32-34 shows three responses to the Gospel. The Gospel is like bitter gourd — it brings out the...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"bitter-gourds-and-honey-for-the-soul\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Bitter Gourds and Honey for the Soul</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/bitter-gourds-and-honey-for-the-soul\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-07-17</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Acts 17:32-34 shows three responses to the Gospel. The Gospel is like bitter gourd — it brings out the worst in you — and like honey — it brings comfort to those who have it worst.</p>\n<h1 id=\"the-gospel-as-bitter-gourd\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Gospel as Bitter Gourd</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Hearing you are sinful, that your religion and good works are harming you, makes you defensive. You think ill of the preacher, presume he doesn&#39;t know you.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">But:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>It hurts because it&#39;s true</li>\n<li>It&#39;s in the Bible</li>\n<li>Deep down, you know it&#39;s true</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;You become defensive because the Gospel shows you the worse side of you, and you don&#39;t like it.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"the-gospel-as-honey\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Gospel as Honey</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Good News comes after the bad news. Jesus Christ has come to save sinners. He died for your sins, rose again from the dead.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Two questions to consider:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>If this were not true, what other hope do you have?</li>\n<li>Why would Jesus die for you if you don&#39;t need it?</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;What a marvelous truth, that Thou my God should think of me and die for me.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"three-responses-acts-17-32-34\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Three Responses (Acts 17:32-34)</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Some mocked</strong> — Defensive, rejecting the message</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Some said &quot;We will hear you again&quot;</strong> — Curious but noncommittal</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Some joined him and believed</strong> — Dionysius, Damaris, and others</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"practical-actions-for-listeners\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Practical Actions for Listeners</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Don&#39;t be shocked with your resistance</strong> — Your heart will try to convince you that you don&#39;t need the Gospel. Listen anyway.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Don&#39;t be cynical with the outcome</strong> — Don&#39;t just &quot;try&quot; to believe. Believe Him who promised.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Believe the Gospel as you would eat and drink without strength</strong> — You don&#39;t need to be taught to eat when hungry. Just believe.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=atonement</a> — The Gospel message</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=witness</a> — Sharing the Gospel</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=faith</a> — Believing the message</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=faith</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=atonement</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
