      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "general",
      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/courted-by-a-good-zombie\nPublished: 2024-12-03 --- A fictional \"Dear Darla\" letter addressing a Christian young woman being courted by an unbeliever who is \"a good...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"courted-by-a-good-zombie\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Courted by a Good Zombie</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/courted-by-a-good-zombie\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-12-03</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">A fictional &quot;Dear Darla&quot; letter addressing a Christian young woman being courted by an unbeliever who is &quot;a good man.&quot; The article addresses three common reasons Christians give for entertaining courtship with unbelievers.</p>\n<h1 id=\"three-reasons-refuted\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Three Reasons Refuted</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">&quot;Is it wrong for him to court me?&quot;</strong> — He is not sinning to court you. But the command to not be unequally yoked (2 Corinthians 6:14) was given to the believer, not the unbeliever. The problem is with you, not him.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">&quot;Why not share the Gospel to him?&quot;</strong> — Yes, the church should share the Gospel with him. But church members who glare are glaring not because he is an unbeliever, but because their sister is sinning by being unequally yoked and bringing him to church unrepentantly.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">&quot;My parents don&#39;t mind&quot;</strong> — Parents often approve even when they don&#39;t approve, knowing rebellion will happen anyway. If parents truly approve unbiblically, creaturely authority is overruled by God&#39;s command (Acts 5:29).</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"key-insight\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Insight</h1>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;He is a good man, sure, but according to God, at best you are being courted by a good zombie.&quot;</blockquote>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">An unbeliever is spiritually dead (Ephesians 2:1-3). The husband God wants for you leads in love like Christ — sacrificing so his bride may be saved, sanctifying her through the Word. An unbeliever cannot do this.</p>\n<h1 id=\"what-to-do\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">What to do</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Confess entertaining the courtship as sin</li>\n<li>Repent — say &#39;no&#39; clearly, don&#39;t string him along</li>\n<li>Seek counsel and accountability with an older married sister in the Lord</li>\n<li>Talk to your pastor about the young man — he needs the Gospel</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=courtship</a> — Intentional, marriage-oriented pursuit governed by God&#39;s Word</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=biblical-manhood</a> — Defined by faithfulness, courage, and commitment</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sin</a> — Unequal yoking as disobedience, not romance</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=courtship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=biblical-manhood</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
