      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "faith",
      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/ditch-the-cobweb-bible\nPublished: 2024-08-06 --- Why do Christians have Bibles gathering cobwebs on their shelves? We take it for granted because it has been freely...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"ditch-the-cobweb-bible\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Ditch the Cobweb Bible</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/ditch-the-cobweb-bible\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-08-06</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Why do Christians have Bibles gathering cobwebs on their shelves? We take it for granted because it has been freely given to us. But it was not free — it was paid for by the blood of Christian forefathers who copied it by hand, evading persecution, hiding the books while being thrown to lions.</p>\n<h1 id=\"two-problems-with-a-cobweb-bible\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Two problems with a cobweb Bible</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">It explains why you struggle with sin.</strong> Without God&#39;s Word as daily food (Matthew 4:4), we have access to the Bible but fail to experience its changing power.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;Dusty Bibles lead to dirty lives.&quot; — Howard Hendricks\n&quot;There is dust enough on some of your Bibles to write &#39;damnation&#39; with your fingers.&quot; — <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=charles-spurgeon</a></blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">It explains why you worry much.</strong> Your source of comfort is tucked in your bookshelf. You struggle with anxiety because the YouVersion app is drowned by notifications.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"key-passage\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Passage</h1>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;I have stored up your word in my heart, that I might not sin against you.&quot; — Psalm 119:11</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"historical-context\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Historical Context</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">James White tells of early Christians killed by Roman authorities because they refused to reveal where the Scriptures were hidden. They gave their lives so that we could read God&#39;s Word.</p>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=scripture</a> — The Word of God as the primary means of revival and maturity</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sin</a> — Neglecting Scripture explains ongoing struggle with sin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=trials</a> — Anxiety comes from not feeding on God&#39;s promises</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=scripture</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
