      "domain": "culture",
      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/is-your-churchs-history-written-down\nPublished: 2024-07-30 --- Many churches have no written account of their history. Pictures exist without captions or stories. Old...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"is-your-church-39-s-history-written-down\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Is Your Church&#39;s History Written Down?</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/is-your-churchs-history-written-down\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-07-30</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Many churches have no written account of their history. Pictures exist without captions or stories. Old saints are no longer around to tell the stories. We are not recording the stories of the saints.</p>\n<h1 id=\"seven-reasons-to-write-church-history\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Seven Reasons to Write Church History</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">It is a biblical practice</strong> — God told Israel to put up altars as reminders. Psalm 102:18: &quot;Let this be recorded for a generation to come.&quot;</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Some stories and people are worth remembering</strong> — A founding pastor&#39;s life and work should not be forgotten by new members.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Recount God&#39;s specific acts of faithfulness</strong> — How the church weathered trials, provided during the pandemic, and cared for members.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Bring joy and laughter in difficult times</strong> — Remembering good old days can encourage during struggles.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Course-correct drift from mission</strong> — Writing history helps remember original priorities and revive fervor.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Encouragement for grandchildren and great-grandchildren</strong> — Future generations will stand on shoulders of giants.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Show a beautiful tapestry of God&#39;s ongoing faithfulness</strong> — An overview allows you to see the pattern across decades.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"how-to-write-church-history\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">How to Write Church History</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Interview long-time members</li>\n<li>Visit church archives — photo albums, old videos, Facebook posts</li>\n<li>Interview pastors and elders</li>\n<li>Write short stories from interviews, not just chronology</li>\n<li>Write a chronological overview too — milestones, buildings, pastors</li>\n<li>Keep writing and store safely</li>\n<li>Publish some stories — website, Facebook throwback posts</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=storytelling</a> — Narrative as the medium of formation</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=church-unity</a> — Shared history binds generations</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ministry</a> — Church life and leadership</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=storytelling</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ministry</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
