      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "general",
      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/little-by-little-everyday\nPublished: 2024-05-16 --- Why are there long lines at lotto counters? Why are casinos never short of customers? Everyone wants wealth quickly....",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"little-by-little-everyday\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Little by Little Everyday</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/little-by-little-everyday\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-05-16</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Why are there long lines at lotto counters? Why are casinos never short of customers? Everyone wants wealth quickly. But Proverbs 13:11 says:</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;Wealth gained hastily will dwindle, but whoever gathers little by little will increase it.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"three-reasons-hasty-wealth-fails\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Three Reasons Hasty Wealth Fails</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">It gives the illusion that wealth won&#39;t dwindle quickly</strong> — Lotto winners often spend wantonly, thinking the amount is inexhaustible.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">It attracts people who want to gain wealth from you</strong> — Relatives and friends come asking for favors, draining resources.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">It doesn&#39;t develop work habits</strong> — The person only knows reaping, not sowing. Without knowing how to sow, save, and invest, resources diminish.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"why-little-by-little-works\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Why Little by Little Works</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">A person with minimum wage learns to budget, maximizing each peso. This builds skills and wisdom. Over time, through hard work and faithfulness, wealth increases.</p>\n<h1 id=\"practical-steps\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Practical Steps</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Start by tithing faithfully</li>\n<li>Set aside savings little by little</li>\n<li>Be faithful in your present work, even if it seems small</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=wisdom</a> — Built over time through fear of the Lord and diligence</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=providence</a> — God&#39;s way often involves slow growth</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=faith</a> — Trusting God&#39;s process rather than seeking shortcuts</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=wisdom</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=faith</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
