      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "ministry",
      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/musings-about-god-gen-zs-and-godly\nPublished: 2024-06-24 --- Four learnings from a youth camp with 144 Gen Z participants. Theme: \"Restored.\" God's promises and power...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"musings-about-god-gen-zs-and-godly-leadership\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Musings About God, Gen-Zs, and Godly Leadership</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/musings-about-god-gen-zs-and-godly\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-06-24</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Four learnings from a youth camp with 144 Gen Z participants. Theme: &quot;Restored.&quot;</p>\n<h1 id=\"musing-no-1-your-past-and-performances-don-39-t-define-your-restoration\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Musing No. 1: Your past and performances don&#39;t define your restoration</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">God&#39;s promises and power do. When we sin repeatedly, we try to restore ourselves before drawing back to God. But restoration comes not by trying better, but by trusting Christ.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;Fix your eyes not on your performance, but on the promises of Christ.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"musing-no-2-impactful-youth-camps-in-the-past-produce-impactful-camps-of-the-present\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Musing No. 2: Impactful youth camps in the past produce impactful camps of the present</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Former campers become camp staff. They ensure the legacy continues — preaching, 1-on-1 counseling, discipleship. Consistency in what honors God matters more than innovation.</p>\n<h1 id=\"musing-no-3-god-39-s-providence-is-better-than-man-39-s-plans\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Musing No. 3: God&#39;s providence is better than man&#39;s plans</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Rain changed the camp&#39;s schedule. The reversed order of activities ended up better than the original plan.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Two truths for leaders:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>God&#39;s providence is better than man&#39;s plans</li>\n<li>Be sober-minded in all situations — make decisions based on godly counsel, not feelings</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;You can be assured that your decision will be sound if you based your decisions on godly counsel rather than on what you feel about your circumstances.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"musing-no-4-gen-z-ers-may-not-be-as-different-as-we-think\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Musing No. 4: Gen Z-ers may not be as different as we think</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Young people can listen to long preaching if they sense the preacher is:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Being honest</li>\n<li>Being truthful</li>\n<li>Really concerned for them</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">They need vulnerable preachers who love them enough to point them to Christ. They also need godly counselors who will sit, listen, challenge, and pray for them.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;Gen-Zers are similar to us in that they need the vulnerable preaching of God&#39;s Word coming forth from the pulpit Sunday after Sunday.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=youth-camps</a> — Discipleship through camping ministry</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=pastoral-ministry</a> — Preaching and counseling</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=providence</a> — God&#39;s plans over ours</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=youth-camps</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=pastoral-ministry</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
