      "created": "Wed Apr 15 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "updated": "Wed Apr 15 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "general",
      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/redeeming-troubled-people\nPublished: 2024-12-18 --- Ruth 4 shows that for people in trouble, God provides a Redeemer. Naomi and Ruth's future depended on someone...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"redeeming-troubled-people\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Redeeming Troubled People</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/redeeming-troubled-people\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-12-18</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Ruth 4 shows that for people in trouble, God provides a Redeemer.</p>\n<h1 id=\"three-realities-for-troubled-people\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Three Realities for Troubled People</h1>\n<h1 id=\"reality-1-we-all-have-troubles-where-we-need-help\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Reality 1: We all have troubles where we need help</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Naomi and Ruth&#39;s future depended on someone redeeming them. They were honest and humble enough to ask Boaz for help — a trait many Christians lack.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Two tells that you need help:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>You publicly sink into immorality in response to your troubles</li>\n<li>You meticulously hide your problem</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"reality-2-we-all-have-something-we-trust-that-fails-us\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Reality 2: We all have something we trust that fails us</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">The nearer redeemer wanted the benefit of Naomi&#39;s property but not the responsibility of caring for her and Ruth. We often trust things that cannot actually help — work, friends, distractions — but they fail to address troubles rooted in the heart.</p>\n<h1 id=\"reality-3-god-has-not-left-us-without-a-redeemer\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Reality 3: God has not left us without a Redeemer</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Boaz committed to redeem Ruth. Through him:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>They were saved from present troubles — provision and protection</li>\n<li>They were saved from long-term troubles — lineage continued through Obed</li>\n<li>They were saved from eternal troubles — Obed → Jesse → David → Jesus</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"the-ultimate-redeemer\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Ultimate Redeemer</h1>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;Jesus is the redeemer who is willing to bear your burden... He is the redeemer who is willing to pay the price of your sin, so that you won&#39;t be slaves to your sin anymore.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=atonement</a> — Christ as the ultimate Redeemer</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=providence</a> — God&#39;s provision of Boaz</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=faith</a> — Trusting the Redeemer</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=atonement</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=faith</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
