      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "ministry",
      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/ruh-ruhs-from-a-36-year-old-minister\nPublished: 2024-07-08 --- Reflections and advice for young men in their 20s looking to serve God. 1. Know God more day after day —...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"ruh-ruhs-from-a-36-year-old-minister\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Ruh-Ruhs From A 36 Year-Old Minister</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/ruh-ruhs-from-a-36-year-old-minister\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-07-08</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Reflections and advice for young men in their 20s looking to serve God.</p>\n<h1 id=\"foundation\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Foundation</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Know God more day after day</strong> — If your knowledge of God in your 20s is the same as when you were a youth, you are not growing.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Guard your intimacy with God</strong> — It&#39;s often the first to go. Use whatever time you have — even 15 minutes — to draw near to God.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Prayer and Bible reading are essential</strong> — Your goal is not performance, it is discovery — discovering more of who God is.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Fellowship regularly with church members</strong> — Start friendships despite awkwardness. Go for coffee, invite them to your home.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"ministry-in-church\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Ministry in Church</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Learn to say yes</strong> — Say yes when it&#39;s about serving God. Say yes to things that make you worried and dependent on God for wisdom.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Learn to say no</strong> — Say no when saying yes forces you to say no to God-given priorities (family, health).</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Don&#39;t worry about failure, worry about pride</strong> — Pride keeps you from saying yes, makes you run away, whispers you to plagiarize.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"on-work\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">On Work</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Show up</strong> — Faithfulness is baked in the ovens of the mundane.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Have multiple streams of income</strong> — Start a side business. Partner with friends. Be willing to fail and start again.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Build bridges, not walls</strong> — Get to know neighbors, gym regulars, coffee shop patrons.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Be creative, not enslaved</strong> — Think of ways to start a business, not just work for others.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Pay off your debts</strong> — Tithe first (don&#39;t go into debt with God), then pay debts transparently.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Be balanced, not idolatrous</strong> — Don&#39;t make work an idol. Rest is a command.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"relationships\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Relationships</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">If single, take risks in courting</strong> — You won&#39;t know unless you ask. Don&#39;t be melodramatic about heartbreaks.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">If in a relationship, surround yourself with older counselors</strong> — They can pray, mediate, treat you to meals.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">&quot;The gift of singleness&quot;</strong> — You probably don&#39;t have it. Celibacy is a gift; singleness is a state.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"yourself\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Yourself</h1>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Stop porn</strong> — It will kill you, your relationship, and your ministry.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Stop lying</strong> — Be honest and vulnerable with someone trustworthy.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Start building</strong> — Build something real, not virtual achievements.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Start attacking</strong> — Don&#39;t just defend against trials. Go on mission.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=wisdom</a> — Practical guidance for young men</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=biblical-manhood</a> — Faithfulness, courage, commitment</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ministry</a> — Serving God faithfully</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=wisdom</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=biblical-manhood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ministry</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
