      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/what-we-are-is-known-to-god\nPublished: 2024-11-25 --- 2 Corinthians 5:11: \"What we are is known to God.\" Are you comfortable with God knowing you? These words are both...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"what-we-are-is-known-to-god\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">What We Are is Known to God</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/what-we-are-is-known-to-god\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-11-25</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">2 Corinthians 5:11: &quot;What we are is known to God.&quot; Are you comfortable with God knowing you? These words are both comfort and warning.</p>\n<h1 id=\"three-truths\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Three Truths</h1>\n<h1 id=\"1-they-are-true-words\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">1. They are true words</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">God knows you — created you, called you, conforms you, cares for you. You are where you are because He brought you there, whether through hard work or through your own sin.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;Where you are now, He knows.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"2-they-are-sobering-words\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">2. They are sobering words</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">You cannot hide your faults and failures from God. He sees through the mask. He sees your porn use, your bitterness, your unforgiving spirit, your secret relationships. He judges not by your good works, but by your sins.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;We have caseloads of sin in us, waiting to be punished.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"3-they-can-be-comforting-words-for-the-christian\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">3. They can be comforting words for the Christian</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">It says &quot;what we are&quot; — not &quot;what we will be.&quot; God saved us not because of our potential, but despite what we are now.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;For while we were still weak, at the right time Christ died for the ungodly.&quot; — Romans 5:6-8</blockquote>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">He knows the worst of us, yet He has not rescinded His calling. He has not stopped sanctifying us. He has not said &quot;you&#39;ve had your chance.&quot;</p>\n<h1 id=\"key-comfort\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Comfort</h1>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;He knows you now, yet He is not letting you go.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=providence</a> — God&#39;s sovereign knowledge and care</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sin</a> — What He knows about us</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sanctification</a> — What He continues to do despite what He knows</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=providence</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sin</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
