      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "work",
      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/when-you-get-your-calling\nPublished: 2024-12-20 --- What happens when your calling is totally different from what you envisioned? Titus Jr wanted to be an art director,...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"when-you-get-your-calling\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">When You Get Your Calling</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/when-you-get-your-calling\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-12-20</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">What happens when your calling is totally different from what you envisioned? Titus Jr wanted to be an art director, creating ads and putting up &quot;Christ is Lord&quot; billboards. Instead, he became a pastor and nonprofit executive.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">John the Baptist&#39;s story (Luke 1:76) shows two lessons about calling.</p>\n<h1 id=\"two-lessons\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Two Lessons</h1>\n<h1 id=\"1-god-39-s-calling-was-all-about-god-not-about-the-called\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">1. God&#39;s calling was all about God, not about the called</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">John was to be a prophet — a mouthpiece. He didn&#39;t get to add his own opinions. He proclaimed what God said.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;Yes, at the end of his life, John wouldn&#39;t have a tombstone that would say, &#39;Here lies John the Baptist, smarter than Einstein.&#39; Yet, I don&#39;t think he would trade his calling.&quot;</blockquote>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Your calling is ultimately about God, not about displaying your smartness or talent.</p>\n<h1 id=\"2-god-39-s-calling-is-the-greatest-good-you-can-do\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">2. God&#39;s calling is the greatest good you can do</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">John&#39;s calling was to prepare the way of the Lord. He would call people to repent for the Messiah was coming.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;As His people, we will be called to do something good by God, no matter what that calling may look like.&quot;</blockquote>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">The good you are called to do is the greatest good you can do. If you are a baker, bake excellent bread. If you are a coder, code good programs. If you are a mother, nurture godly children.</p>\n<h1 id=\"key-insight\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Insight</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Callings can change. Where you are right now is most likely where He wants you to do good, until He brings you somewhere else.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;God doesn&#39;t make mistakes of where He puts you. Serve Him with gladness, for it&#39;s all about Him.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=providence</a> — God&#39;s placement of us</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=work</a> — Vocation and calling</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ministry</a> — God&#39;s calling to serve</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=work</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=providence</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
