      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "general",
      "excerpt": "Source: titus-jr-laxa — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/you-yourself-will-seek\nPublished: 2024-12-11 --- A devotional poem on Ezekiel 34:11-16, reflecting on God as the Shepherd who seeks His scattered sheep. \"For thus says...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"you-yourself-will-seek\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">You Yourself Will Seek</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — tituslaxajr.substack.com/p/you-yourself-will-seek\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2024-12-11</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">A devotional poem on Ezekiel 34:11-16, reflecting on God as the Shepherd who seeks His scattered sheep.</p>\n<h1 id=\"key-passage\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Passage</h1>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;For thus says the Lord God: Behold, I, I myself will search for my sheep and will seek them out.&quot; — Ezekiel 34:11</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"the-shepherd-39-s-actions\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Shepherd&#39;s Actions</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Search</strong> — God Himself seeks out His scattered sheep</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Rescue</strong> — From all places where they have been scattered</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Bring out</strong> — From peoples and countries into their own land</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Feed</strong> — On the mountains of Israel, in good pasture</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Bind up</strong> — The injured</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Strengthen</strong> — The weak</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Destroy</strong> — The fat and strong (the false shepherds who oppressed)</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"the-poem\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Poem</h1>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">Lord, have we not countless times gone astray,\nLike sheep without a shepherd we have gone our way,\nAs we have gone the light end up waned,\nIn the darkness broken, weakened and pained.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Yet while we were far off You were there,\nAmong the scattered You were tender with care,\nYou became the Shepherd your sheep needed be,\nYou came to us one by one, and brought us to Thee.</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"fulfillment\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Fulfillment</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Jesus is the Good Shepherd who fulfills Ezekiel 34. He seeks the lost, brings back the strayed, binds up the injured, strengthens the weak.</p>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=atonement</a> — Christ as the Shepherd who lays down His life</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=providence</a> — God seeking us before we seek Him</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=restoring-broken-people</a> — God&#39;s restoration of the scattered</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources-updated\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources Updated</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=atonement</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=providence</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
