      "created": "Wed Apr 15 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "updated": "Wed Apr 15 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "general",
      "excerpt": "Brokenness is being unable to do what God calls you to do because of what's going on inside you. It is being overcome with fear, bitterness, and unbelief to the point that you can no longer function in that area. From...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"brokenness\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Brokenness</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Brokenness is being unable to do what God calls you to do because of what&#39;s going on inside you. It is being overcome with fear, bitterness, and unbelief to the point that you can no longer function in that area.</p>\n<h1 id=\"signs-of-brokenness\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Signs of Brokenness</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">From <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=restoring-broken-people</a>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Possessed by a spirit of fear</strong> — No longer wanting people around; expecting evil</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Overwhelmed by a spirit of bitterness</strong> — Anger, hatred, mumbling at your own situation</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Filled with a spirit of unbelief</strong> — No longer believing in God&#39;s revealed character</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"struggles-with-brokenness\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Struggles with Brokenness</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">It happens to anyone</strong> — Tragedies, troubles, and transgression can happen to the best of us</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Nothing seems to fix it</strong> — Changing location or people doesn&#39;t work; the brokenness comes with you</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"salvation-from-brokenness\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Salvation from Brokenness</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">To be restored means to repair what is broken and make it as if it is not broken.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Signs of restoration:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Finding courage again</li>\n<li>Starting to obey again</li>\n<li>Starting to believe again</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">How God restores:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Through His kindness</li>\n<li>Through His presence</li>\n<li>Through His promises</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=lament</a> — Honest grief before God</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=trials</a> — Suffering that exposes brokenness</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sanctification</a> — God&#39;s restoration work</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=restoring-broken-people</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
