      "sources": 2,
      "domain": "faith",
      "excerpt": "Confession is calling out sin by name, with the same name God uses to describe it in Scripture. It is being honest with our sin without qualification or excuse. - Not minimizing — \"I just made a mistake\"\n- Not reframing...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"confession\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Confession</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Confession is calling out sin by name, with the same name God uses to describe it in Scripture. It is being honest with our sin without qualification or excuse.</p>\n<h1 id=\"what-confession-is-not\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">What Confession Is Not</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Not minimizing</strong> — &quot;I just made a mistake&quot;</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Not reframing</strong> — &quot;We all struggle&quot;</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Not hiding</strong> — Covering with fig leaves (Genesis 3)</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Not excusing</strong> — &quot;I did it because I was hurt&quot;</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"what-confession-is\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">What Confession Is</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">From <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=is-god-angry-with-you-thats-ok</a>:</p>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;Confession of sin is calling out our sin by name, with the same name God uses to describe it in Scripture. It means being honest with our sin.&quot;</blockquote>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">From <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=vanilla-ice-cream-over-cow-dung</a>:</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">The opposite of hiding is confession. Adam and Eve hid with fig leaves and excuses. God provided garments of skin — a sacrifice was involved. Christ is the Lamb of God who takes away sin.</p>\n<h1 id=\"the-promise\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Promise</h1>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;If we confess our sins, he is faithful and just to forgive us our sins and to cleanse us from all unrighteousness.&quot; — 1 John 1:9</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sin</a> — What we confess</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=repentance</a> — Turning from sin</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=atonement</a> — The basis for forgiveness</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=is-god-angry-with-you-thats-ok</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=vanilla-ice-cream-over-cow-dung</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
