      "created": "Wed Apr 15 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "updated": "Wed Apr 15 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "ministry",
      "excerpt": "Youth camps are intensive discipleship experiences for young people, typically involving preaching, small groups, recreation, and personal counseling. - Centrality of preaching — Multiple sessions teaching God's Word\n-...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"youth-camps\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Youth Camps</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Youth camps are intensive discipleship experiences for young people, typically involving preaching, small groups, recreation, and personal counseling.</p>\n<h1 id=\"key-elements\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Elements</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Centrality of preaching</strong> — Multiple sessions teaching God&#39;s Word</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">One-on-one counseling</strong> — Personal discipleship and prayer</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Team building</strong> — Activities that build relationships</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Legacy continuity</strong> — Former campers become camp staff</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"observations-from-practice\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Observations from Practice</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">From <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=musings-about-god-gen-zs-and-godly-leadership</a>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">God&#39;s grace, not performance, defines restoration</strong> — Young people don&#39;t need to &quot;fix themselves&quot; before coming to God</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Impactful camps produce future leaders</strong> — The core activities that honor God should remain consistent: preaching, counseling, discipleship</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Providence over plans</strong> — Leaders must be sober-minded when plans change due to circumstances</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Gen Z still needs preaching and counseling</strong> — Young people can engage with long preaching if they sense the preacher is honest, truthful, and concerned for them</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=pastoral-ministry</a> — Preaching and counseling</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=discipleship</a> — Life-on-life investment</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=providence</a> — Trusting God when plans change</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=musings-about-god-gen-zs-and-godly-leadership</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
