      "excerpt": "Pastor and writer. Writes at thisisfoster.com on topics including Christian family life, culture, sexuality, and parenting. Studied human sexuality at Northern Kentucky University...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"michael-foster\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Michael Foster</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Pastor and writer. Writes at <strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">thisisfoster.com</strong> on topics including Christian family life, culture, sexuality, and parenting. Studied human sexuality at Northern Kentucky University. Takes a Reformed, culturally engaged approach — willing to address uncomfortable topics (pornography, erotic fiction, parenting failures) from a pastoral perspective.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">His wife teaches on household management, meal planning, and family rhythms. Her teaching appears in edited form on his Substack.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"appearances-in-wiki\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Appearances in wiki</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=normalization-of-female-sexual-degeneracy</a> — critique of romance/erotic fiction as female pornography; the removal of shame</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=some-thoughts-on-parenting-part-2</a> — storytelling as the central practice of godly parenting</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=a-common-danger-in-house-churches</a> — dangers of unaccountable leadership and restorationist delusion in house church movements</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=how-influencer-culture-destroys-pastors</a> — platform over people; the craft of pastoring vs. influencer culture</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=mature-masculinity</a> — summary of 1 Timothy 3 traits; self-rule under Christ&#39;s lordship</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=my-current-approach-to-ai</a> — partition, not balance; use the machine but don&#39;t live inside it</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=the-rhythm-of-the-household</a> — his wife&#39;s teaching on household rhythms (edited transcript)</li>\n</ul>\n",
