      "excerpt": "Length: Full lens breakdown, no length limit --- Complete documentation of each lens's analysis. This is the full reasoning behind the executive summary. --- Question: [The research question]\nScope: [What's in and out]...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"deep-dive\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Deep Dive</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Length</strong>: Full lens breakdown, no length limit</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"purpose\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Purpose</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Complete documentation of each lens&#39;s analysis. This is the full reasoning behind the executive summary.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"structure\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Structure</h1>\n<h1 id=\"research-context\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Research Context</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**Question**: [The research question]\n**Scope**: [What's in and out]\n**Time Horizon**: [Past/present/future range]\n**Decision Goal**: [What decision this informs]</code></pre>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"lens-findings\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Lens Findings</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">For each lens (in order):</p>\n<h1 id=\"technical-lens\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Technical Lens</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**Mechanism**: [How it works]\n\n**Data**: [What the numbers say]\n\n**Systems View**: [Feedback loops, bottlenecks]\n\n**Technical Gaps**: [What we don't know]\n\n**Confidence**: [High/Medium/Low]\n\n**Contradictions**: [Where this conflicts with other lenses]\n\n**Sources**: [Citations]</code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"economic-lens\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Economic Lens</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**Incentive Structure**: [Who wants what and why]\n\n**Money Flows**: [Where money comes from and goes]\n\n**Market Dynamics**: [Competition, barriers, pricing power]\n\n**Externalities**: [Who bears hidden costs]\n\n**Confidence**: [High/Medium/Low]\n\n**Contradictions**: [Where this conflicts with other lenses]\n\n**Sources**: [Citations]</code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"historical-lens\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Historical Lens</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**Precedents**: [What happened before]\n\n**Patterns**: [Cycles and trends]\n\n**Causes**: [How we got here]\n\n**Lessons**: [What history teaches]\n\n**Confidence**: [High/Medium/Low]\n\n**Contradictions**: [Where this conflicts with other lenses]\n\n**Sources**: [Citations]</code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"geopolitical-lens\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Geopolitical Lens</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**Power Distribution**: [Who decides, vetoes, implements]\n\n**Interests**: [What each actor wants]\n\n**Alliances**: [Who aligns with whom, fault lines]\n\n**Geographic Factors**: [Location, choke points, resources]\n\n**Narratives**: [Stories that legitimize power]\n\n**Confidence**: [High/Medium/Low]\n\n**Contradictions**: [Where this conflicts with other lenses]\n\n**Sources**: [Citations]</code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"contrarian-lens\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Contrarian Lens</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**Consensus View**: [What everyone believes]\n\n**Challenge**: [Why it might be wrong]\n\n**Alternative Framing**: [Different way to see this]\n\n**Stress Test**: [What would change minds]\n\n**Confidence**: [High/Medium/Low]\n\n**Contradictions**: [Where this conflicts with other lenses]\n\n**Sources**: [Citations]</code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"first-principles-lens\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">First Principles Lens</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**Component Parts**: [What it's made of]\n\n**Ground Truths**: [What we know for certain]\n\n**Rebuilt Model**: [What follows from fundamentals]\n\n**Divergences**: [Where model differs from observed reality]\n\n**Confidence**: [High/Medium/Low]\n\n**Contradictions**: [Where this conflicts with other lenses]\n\n**Sources**: [Citations]</code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"reformed-theological-lens\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Reformed Theological Lens</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**Scriptural Teaching**: [What Scripture says or implies]\n\n**Sin Analysis**: [How fallen nature distorts this]\n\n**Sovereignty View**: [God's control vs. human responsibility]\n\n**Eternal Perspective**: [What lasts, what passes]\n\n**Moral Judgment**: [Right, wrong, indifferent, wisdom required]\n\n**Confidence**: [High/Medium/Low]\n\n**Contradictions**: [Where this conflicts with other lenses]\n\n**Sources**: [Citations]</code></pre>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"contradictions-log\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Contradictions Log</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">All contradictions surfaced during lens analysis:</p>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>### Contradiction 1\n**Lenses**: [Which lenses conflict]\n**Type**: [Scope/Value/Uncertainty/Genuine]\n**Analysis**: [Why they conflict]\n**Resolution**: [How handled]\n\n[Repeat for each contradiction]</code></pre>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"synthesis\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Synthesis</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Follow <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=synthesis-rules</a>:</p>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**Highest Confidence Findings**: [Facts that multiple lenses confirm]\n\n**Key Tradeoffs**: [Where lenses conflict and how to navigate]\n\n**Theological Boundary**: [What Scripture permits, requires, or forbids]\n\n**Recommendation**: [Clear judgment with confidence level]\n\n**What Would Change This**: [Evidence that would shift the recommendation]</code></pre>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"source-list\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Source List</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Complete list of all sources cited, organized by:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Primary sources</li>\n<li>Expert secondary sources</li>\n<li>Quality journalism</li>\n<li>Other</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Each source includes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Full citation</li>\n<li>Tier rating (1-5)</li>\n<li>How it was used</li>\n</ul>\n",
