      "created": "Wed Apr 15 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "updated": "Wed Apr 15 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "sources": 0,
      "domain": "general",
      "excerpt": "Authority: Incentives, money flows --- Who gains? Who pays? --- - People respond to incentives\n- Money flows reveal priorities and power\n- Markets aggregate information (even when imperfect)\n- Efficiency and value...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"economic-lens\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Economic Lens</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Authority</strong>: Incentives, money flows</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"core-question\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Core Question</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Who gains? Who pays?</strong></p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"assumptions\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Assumptions</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>People respond to incentives</li>\n<li>Money flows reveal priorities and power</li>\n<li>Markets aggregate information (even when imperfect)</li>\n<li>Efficiency and value creation are measurable</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"questions-to-ask\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Questions to Ask</h1>\n<h1 id=\"incentives\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Incentives</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Who benefits if this succeeds?</li>\n<li>Who loses if this succeeds?</li>\n<li>Who benefits if this fails?</li>\n<li>What does each actor want?</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"money-flows\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Money Flows</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Where does money come from?</li>\n<li>Where does it go?</li>\n<li>Who captures the margin?</li>\n<li>What are the hidden costs?</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"market-dynamics\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Market Dynamics</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Is this a competitive market or captured?</li>\n<li>What are the barriers to entry?</li>\n<li>Where is pricing power?</li>\n<li>What happens at scale?</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"economic-tradeoffs\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Economic Tradeoffs</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>What is the opportunity cost?</li>\n<li>What are the externalities?</li>\n<li>How are costs and benefits distributed?</li>\n<li>What would rational actors do?</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"typical-sources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Typical Sources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Financial statements and filings</li>\n<li>Market research and industry reports</li>\n<li>Economic analyses and cost-benefit studies</li>\n<li>Supply chain and pricing data</li>\n<li>Incentive structure documentation</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"blind-spots\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Blind Spots</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>May reduce human behavior to rational calculation</li>\n<li>Can miss non-monetary motivations</li>\n<li>May ignore what can&#39;t be measured in dollars</li>\n<li>Assumes efficient markets where they may not exist</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"confidence-signals\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Confidence Signals</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">High confidence</strong>: Clear incentive structures; verified financial data; predictable market dynamics</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Medium confidence</strong>: Incentives are clear but financial data is incomplete; market dynamics are partially understood</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Low confidence</strong>: Incentives are hidden or complex; financial data is unavailable or unreliable; market is distorted or captured</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"output-format\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Output Format</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>### Economic Lens Findings\n\n**Incentive Structure**: [who wants what and why]\n\n**Money Flows**: [where money comes from and goes]\n\n**Market Dynamics**: [competition, barriers, pricing power]\n\n**Externalities**: [who bears hidden costs]\n\n**Confidence**: [high/medium/low]\n\n**Contradictions**: [where this conflicts with other lenses]</code></pre>\n",
