      "domain": "general",
      "excerpt": "Length: ≤500 words --- A concise synthesis that can be read in 2-3 minutes and understood by someone who will not read the full research. --- 1-2 sentences restating the research question and its stakes. [What was asked...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"executive-summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Executive Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Length</strong>: ≤500 words</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"purpose\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Purpose</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">A concise synthesis that can be read in 2-3 minutes and understood by someone who will not read the full research.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"structure\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Structure</h1>\n<h1 id=\"the-question\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Question</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">1-2 sentences restating the research question and its stakes.</p>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>[What was asked and why it matters]</code></pre>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"key-findings\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Findings</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">3-5 bullet points. Each finding should be:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete thought (not a fragment)</li>\n<li>Stated with confidence level</li>\n<li>Supported by multiple lenses where possible</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**[High confidence]** [Finding 1]\n**[Medium confidence]** [Finding 2]\n**[Low confidence]** [Finding 3]</code></pre>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"the-tradeoff\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Tradeoff</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Where lenses conflict, state the core tension in one paragraph.</p>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>[Economic lens says X; theological lens says Y. The tradeoff is Z.]</code></pre>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"recommendation\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Recommendation</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">One clear answer to the original question.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">If the research cannot reach a conclusion, say so and explain why.</p>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>**Recommendation**: [Clear judgment]\n**Confidence**: [High/Medium/Low]\n**What would change this**: [1-2 pieces of evidence that would shift the recommendation]</code></pre>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"style-rules\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Style Rules</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>No jargon without explanation</li>\n<li>No hedging (&quot;somewhat&quot;, &quot;arguably&quot;, &quot;it depends&quot;)</li>\n<li>No &quot;on one hand, on the other hand&quot; without a conclusion</li>\n<li>State findings directly</li>\n<li>Lead with what matters most</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"example\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Example</h1>\n<h1 id=\"the-question\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Question</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Should a church invest in AI-powered translation for its missions conference?</p>\n<h1 id=\"key-findings\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Findings</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">[High confidence]</strong> AI translation is now accurate enough for conference settings when trained on relevant domain text.</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">[High confidence]</strong> The cost is 80% lower than professional human translation.</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">[Medium confidence]</strong> Attendees prefer human translators for relational connection, even when AI is more accurate.</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">[Low confidence]</strong> Long-term effects on missionary language learning are unknown but likely minimal.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"the-tradeoff\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Tradeoff</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Economic and technical lenses strongly favor AI (cost and accuracy). The theological lens raises a concern: is translation a relational ministry or a technical task? If the goal is information transfer, AI works. If the goal is connection, human translators serve better.</p>\n<h1 id=\"recommendation\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Recommendation</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Recommendation</strong>: Use AI translation for plenary sessions and printed materials; retain human translators for small group discussions and pastoral care.\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Confidence</strong>: High\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">What would change this</strong>: Evidence that AI translation significantly harms attendee trust or engagement.</p>\n",
