      "sources": 0,
      "domain": "general",
      "excerpt": "Authority: Patterns, precedents --- What happened before? --- - History doesn't repeat, but it rhymes\n- Present situations have causes in the past\n- Analogies from history can illuminate current decisions\n- Context...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"historical-lens\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Historical Lens</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Authority</strong>: Patterns, precedents</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"core-question\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Core Question</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">What happened before?</strong></p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"assumptions\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Assumptions</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>History doesn&#39;t repeat, but it rhymes</li>\n<li>Present situations have causes in the past</li>\n<li>Analogies from history can illuminate current decisions</li>\n<li>Context matters — same inputs can produce different outputs in different times</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"questions-to-ask\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Questions to Ask</h1>\n<h1 id=\"precedents\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Precedents</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Has this happened before?</li>\n<li>What was similar? What was different?</li>\n<li>What were the outcomes?</li>\n<li>What did contemporaries get wrong?</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"patterns\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Patterns</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>What cycles are visible?</li>\n<li>What trends are accelerating or decelerating?</li>\n<li>What has remained constant?</li>\n<li>What has fundamentally changed?</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"causes\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Causes</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>What led to this situation?</li>\n<li>What decisions created the current state?</li>\n<li>What were the unintended consequences?</li>\n<li>What alternatives were available but not taken?</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"lessons\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Lessons</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>What did people at the time believe?</li>\n<li>What did they miss?</li>\n<li>What would we do differently with hindsight?</li>\n<li>What analogies are valid? Which are misleading?</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"typical-sources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Typical Sources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Historical accounts and archives</li>\n<li>Contemporary records (newspapers, journals, documents)</li>\n<li>Academic histories</li>\n<li>Oral histories and interviews</li>\n<li>Comparative case studies</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"blind-spots\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Blind Spots</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Survivorship bias in what gets recorded</li>\n<li>Presentism — judging past by present standards</li>\n<li>False analogies — surface similarities masking deep differences</li>\n<li>May miss what is genuinely new</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"confidence-signals\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Confidence Signals</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">High confidence</strong>: Multiple independent historical accounts; clear precedents with documented outcomes; patterns hold across multiple cases</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Medium confidence</strong>: Historical record exists but is incomplete; precedents are partial; patterns are suggestive but not definitive</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Low confidence</strong>: Sparse historical record; analogies are speculative; situation is genuinely unprecedented</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"output-format\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Output Format</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>### Historical Lens Findings\n\n**Precedents**: [what happened before]\n\n**Patterns**: [cycles and trends visible]\n\n**Causes**: [how we got here]\n\n**Lessons**: [what history teaches]\n\n**Confidence**: [high/medium/low]\n\n**Contradictions**: [where this conflicts with other lenses]</code></pre>\n",
