      "domain": "general",
      "excerpt": "Authority: Data, systems, mechanisms --- How does it work? --- - Reality is knowable through measurement and analysis\n- Systems follow rules that can be discovered and described\n- The best explanation is the one that...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"technical-lens\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Technical Lens</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Authority</strong>: Data, systems, mechanisms</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"core-question\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Core Question</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">How does it work?</strong></p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"assumptions\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Assumptions</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Reality is knowable through measurement and analysis</li>\n<li>Systems follow rules that can be discovered and described</li>\n<li>The best explanation is the one that most accurately predicts outcomes</li>\n<li>Expertise and technical competence are the primary virtues</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"questions-to-ask\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Questions to Ask</h1>\n<h1 id=\"mechanism\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Mechanism</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>What are the moving parts?</li>\n<li>How do they interact?</li>\n<li>What are the inputs and outputs?</li>\n<li>Where are the leverage points?</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"data\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Data</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>What data exists?</li>\n<li>What data is missing?</li>\n<li>How reliable is the data?</li>\n<li>What does the data actually measure vs. what we want to know?</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"systems\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Systems</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>What are the feedback loops?</li>\n<li>What amplifies? What dampens?</li>\n<li>Where are the bottlenecks?</li>\n<li>What scales? What breaks at scale?</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"technical-debt\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Technical Debt</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>What assumptions are baked in?</li>\n<li>What legacy constraints exist?</li>\n<li>What would a clean-sheet solution look like?</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"typical-sources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Typical Sources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Technical documentation and specifications</li>\n<li>Academic papers in relevant fields</li>\n<li>Expert interviews and practitioner accounts</li>\n<li>Performance data and metrics</li>\n<li>System diagrams and process maps</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"blind-spots\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Blind Spots</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>May miss human factors that don&#39;t show up in data</li>\n<li>Can conflate &quot;measurable&quot; with &quot;important&quot;</li>\n<li>May ignore power dynamics that shape technical choices</li>\n<li>Technical optimization can miss economic or moral questions</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"confidence-signals\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Confidence Signals</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">High confidence</strong>: Multiple independent measurements converge; mechanisms are well-understood; predictions hold across contexts</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Medium confidence</strong>: Data exists but is incomplete; mechanism is plausible but unverified</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Low confidence</strong>: Data is sparse or contested; mechanism is speculative; system is too complex to model</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"output-format\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Output Format</h1>\n<pre class=\"bg-surface-container-low p-6 my-8 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono text-on-surface-variant\"><code>### Technical Lens Findings\n\n**Mechanism**: [how it works]\n\n**Data**: [what the numbers say]\n\n**Systems View**: [feedback loops, bottlenecks]\n\n**Technical Gaps**: [what we don't know technically]\n\n**Confidence**: [high/medium/low]\n\n**Contradictions**: [where this conflicts with other lenses]</code></pre>\n",
