      "domain": "ministry",
      "excerpt": "Biblical principles for planting new churches. --- From \"Church Planting: a Church God can Use\" notes: - Prayer as foundation - Obedience to the Spirit's leading - Leaders released and commissioned - Not just clergy;...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"church-planting\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Church Planting</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Biblical principles for planting new churches.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"a-church-god-can-use\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">A Church God Can Use</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">From &quot;Church Planting: a Church God can Use&quot; notes:</p>\n<h1 id=\"1-a-spiritual-church\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">1. A Spiritual Church</h1>\n<h1 id=\"a-church-39-s-communication-with-god-acts-1-14\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">a. Church&#39;s communication with God (Acts 1:14)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Prayer as foundation</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"b-church-39-s-compliance-to-god-acts-11-21-24-acts-2-37\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">b. Church&#39;s compliance to God (Acts 11:21-24; Acts 2:37)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Obedience to the Spirit&#39;s leading</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"2-a-sending-church\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">2. A Sending Church</h1>\n<h1 id=\"a-church-leaders-acts-13-1-4\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">a. Church Leaders (Acts 13:1-4)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Leaders released and commissioned</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"b-ordinary-members-acts-11-19\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">b. Ordinary Members (Acts 11:19)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Not just clergy; laypeople spread the Word</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"3-a-soaring-church\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">3. A Soaring Church</h1>\n<h1 id=\"a-departure-of-a-team-member-acts-13-13-2-timothy-4-9-16\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">a. Departure of a Team Member (Acts 13:13; 2 Timothy 4:9-16)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Send-offs are part of the process</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"b-the-detractors-of-the-team-acts-14-19-20\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">b. The Detractors of the Team (Acts 14:19-20)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Opposition is expected</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"4-a-selfless-church\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">4. A Selfless Church</h1>\n<h1 id=\"a-the-labor-in-church-planting-1-thess-2-9-17-acts-20-31-rom-16-12-acts-18-3-5\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">a. The Labor in Church Planting (1 Thess. 2:9, 17; Acts 20:31; Rom. 16:12; Acts 18:3-5)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Hard work, tentmaking, sacrificial labor</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"b-the-love-in-church-planting-2-cor-5-14\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">b. The Love in Church Planting (2 Cor. 5:14)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Christ&#39;s love compels</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"purpose-vision-goal\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Purpose, Vision, Goal</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Purpose:</strong> To Love God and People (Mark 12:30-31)</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Vision:</strong> To win souls and make disciples (Matt. 28:19-20)</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Goal:</strong> Every believer a cell leader of cell leaders (2 Timothy 2:2)</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"see-also\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">See Also</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=pastoral-ministry</a> — Shepherding planted churches</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=church-unity</a> — The unity we have and grow toward</li>\n</ul>\n",
