      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "ministry",
      "excerpt": "The biblical pattern for making disciples through life-on-life community. --- From Mark 2:1-12: 1. Diwa ng Pagmamahal sa iba — Leave what you are doing to help someone in need...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"small-groups\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Small Groups</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">The biblical pattern for making disciples through life-on-life community.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"life-sharing-discipleship\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Life-Sharing Discipleship</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">From Mark 2:1-12:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Diwa ng Pagmamahal sa iba</strong> — Leave what you are doing to help someone in need.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Diwa ng Pagkakaisa</strong> — Everyone focus on the task or mission; able to have contact.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">They believe that Jesus is the only answer.</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li><p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Having priority to save a life</strong> — Break the barrier that stands in the way of us doing what we ought to do.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;They were determined. Be strict with our priorities.&quot;</blockquote>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"discipleship-definition\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Discipleship Definition</h1>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;Discipleship = relationship&quot;</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;Disciples = life-sharing process.&quot;</blockquote>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"see-also\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">See Also</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=church-planting</a> — Churches planted through small groups</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=pastoral-ministry</a> — Shepherding through groups</li>\n</ul>\n",
