      "excerpt": "Titus Jr's professional life as an educator and academic program leader at STI College San Fernando, Pampanga. --- Role: BMMA Program Head & Capstone Project Coordinator Courses taught:\n- Multimedia Publishing\n- Film...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"education\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Education</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Titus Jr&#39;s professional life as an educator and academic program leader at STI College San Fernando, Pampanga.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"overview\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Overview</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Role:</strong> BMMA Program Head &amp; Capstone Project Coordinator</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Courses taught:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Multimedia Publishing</li>\n<li>Film Production</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">His academic role puts him at the intersection of media, storytelling, and student formation — themes that echo his ministry and writing.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"current-activity-april-2026\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Current activity (April 2026)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Capstone defenses: April 29 &amp; May 2</li>\n<li>Spectrum of Strength — neurodivergent advocacy event at STI, April 14</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"concepts\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Concepts</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=storytelling</a> — central to both his teaching (film, media) and his theology</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=design-thinking</a> — relevant to multimedia and production courses</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ai-and-faith</a> — AI is pervasive in student life; how to teach and model faithful use</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"projects\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Projects</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=shepherds-shelf</a> — AI-assisted learning tool; extends his interest in structured study</li>\n<li>Self-directed doctoral-level study in Reformed Christian history</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"people\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">People</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"resources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Resources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ai-and-the-christian-life</a> — talk on how Christians (including students) should use AI: tool not idol, heart not hardware, agency not delegation</li>\n</ul>\n",
