      "excerpt": "Spouse of titus-jr-laxa. Based in Singapore. --- - Part of Kapatid Ministry partnership with Titus Jr\n- Based in Singapore, connecting with Filipino diaspora ministry --- - titus-jr-laxa — Spouse\n- ministry — Ministry...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"rezy-laxa\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Rezy Laxa</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Spouse of <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a>. Based in Singapore.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"ministry-involvement\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Ministry Involvement</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Part of Kapatid Ministry partnership with Titus Jr</li>\n<li>Based in Singapore, connecting with Filipino diaspora ministry</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"see-also\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">See Also</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — Spouse</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ministry</a> — Ministry area</li>\n</ul>\n",
