      "excerpt": "The Holy Spirit is the third person of the Trinity, who indwells believers and empowers them for witness and holiness. From empowered-for-a-reason (Acts 1:8): The Holy Spirit empowers believers for:\n- A specific...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"holy-spirit\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Holy Spirit</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">The Holy Spirit is the third person of the Trinity, who indwells believers and empowers them for witness and holiness.</p>\n<h1 id=\"empowerment-for-a-purpose\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Empowerment for a Purpose</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">From <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=empowered-for-a-reason</a> (Acts 1:8):</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">The Holy Spirit empowers believers for:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">A specific assignment</strong> — Power is given for being Jesus&#39;s witnesses, not for personal wishes</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">A specific action</strong> — Being a witness involves knowing Christ, being transformed by Him, and speaking about Him</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;You don&#39;t have the power to change someone, but God has given you the power to remain faithful even if the person is not yet visibly changing.&quot;</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"the-spirit-39-s-role-in-sanctification\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">The Spirit&#39;s Role in Sanctification</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">From <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=young-man-beware-of-taking-placebos</a>:</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Sanctification is an ongoing work that the Holy Spirit begins at salvation and ends at glorification. Some believers are instantaneously set free from certain sins; most grow in victory over time.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Antidote:</strong> Seek the help and power of the Holy Spirit always — in weakness and in strength.</p>\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sanctification</a> — The Spirit&#39;s ongoing work</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=witness</a> — Empowered for testimony</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=evangelism</a> — Power for Gospel proclamation</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=faith</a> — Trusting the Spirit&#39;s power</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=repentance</a> — The Spirit grants repentance (2 Timothy 2:25)</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=empowered-for-a-reason</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=young-man-beware-of-taking-placebos</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
