      "excerpt": "Titus Jr's pastoral and missions life — preaching, church planting, youth work, and mission coordination. --- Titus Jr serves as a pastor with Reformed Baptist leanings. He is active in multiple ministry contexts: -...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"ministry\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Ministry</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Titus Jr&#39;s pastoral and missions life — preaching, church planting, youth work, and mission coordination.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"overview\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Overview</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Titus Jr serves as a pastor with Reformed Baptist leanings. He is active in multiple ministry contexts:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Kapatid Ministry, Inc. (KMI)</strong> — CEO; coordinates mission trips, child sponsorship, diaspora ministry</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Local Baptist churches</strong> — preaching, youth ministry, children&#39;s ministry across multiple church plants</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Diaspora ministry</strong> — connection to Filipino OFWs through Rezy in Singapore</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"concepts\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Concepts</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=faith</a> — theological foundation of pastoral work</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=worship</a> — liturgy and the Lord&#39;s Day as formation</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sanctification</a> — the primary concern of pastoral preaching</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=prayer</a> — the backbone of pastoral life and ministry</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=pastoral-ministry</a> — the craft of shepherding human souls</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=church-accountability</a> — plural eldership, tested character</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sola-scriptura</a> — Scripture alone as ultimate authority</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=church-unity</a> — the unity we have and the unity we grow toward</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=calling</a> — God&#39;s placement for His purposes; ultimately about God, not us</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=church-planting</a> — biblical principles for planting new churches</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=small-groups</a> — life-on-life discipleship through community</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=tentmaking</a> — marketplace missions: professional skills as avenue for Gospel ministry</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"projects\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Projects</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=stewardtrack</a> — SaaS tool for church management</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"people\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">People</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — Author and pastor</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=rezy-laxa</a> — Spouse, Singapore connection</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=michael-foster</a> — pastor and writer on pastoral ministry</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=douglas-wilson</a> — Reformed pastor and theologian</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"resources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Resources</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Sermon preparation and ministry talks ingested:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=crucified-with-christ</a> — Romans 6:6: the believer&#39;s co-crucifixion with Christ</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=level-up</a> — Colossians 2:6-7: God levels up faith through increasing demands</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=life-in-between</a> — Genesis 1:27-28: God&#39;s design for work, sexuality, fruitfulness</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ai-and-the-christian-life</a> — Pastoral talk on AI use</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=a-common-danger-in-house-churches</a> — Dangers of unaccountable leadership</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=how-influencer-culture-destroys-pastors</a> — Platform vs. people</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ruh-ruhs-from-a-36-year-old-minister</a> — Wisdom for young adults in ministry: know God, guard intimacy, serve faithfully</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"see-also\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">See Also</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=work</a> — Professional design work supporting ministry</li>\n</ul>\n",
