      "domain": "general",
      "excerpt": "Life domain covering marriage, family, friendships, and courtship. --- Biblical Foundation (Ephesians 5:22-33) Wives submit to your own husband:\n- Submit as to the Lord (Eph. 5:22)\n- Submit in everything (Eph...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"relationships\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Relationships</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Life domain covering marriage, family, friendships, and courtship.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"marriage\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Marriage</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Biblical Foundation</strong> (Ephesians 5:22-33)</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Wives submit to your own husband:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Submit as to the Lord (Eph. 5:22)</li>\n<li>Submit in everything (Eph. 5:24)</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Husbands love your wives (agape):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Forfeit personal rights</li>\n<li>Focus on giving, not getting</li>\n<li>Forgive personal offenses</li>\n<li>As Christ loved the Church (Eph. 5:25-27)</li>\n<li>As their own body (Eph. 5:28, 31)</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"household-rhythms\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Household Rhythms</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">The recurring patterns that regulate daily life: when people sleep and wake, when they eat, how the home is kept, and what the family does together.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Four rhythms:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Daily</strong> — wake time, meal times, bedtime</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Weekly</strong> — meal planning, family night</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Maintenance</strong> — zones, chores, tidying vs. cleaning</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Habits</strong> — precedents, expectations, character</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">Children are like olive shoots. Mothers are like trellises. Our job is to guide the growth in the right direction while the plant is still pliable.</blockquote>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">See <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=household-rhythms</a> for detailed framework.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"courtship\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Courtship</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Key principles:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Intentional, marriage-oriented pursuit</li>\n<li>God&#39;s will as central question</li>\n<li>Community involvement (parents, kapatids)</li>\n<li>Clear programme and commitments</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">See <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=courtship</a> for detailed framework.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"unequally-yoked\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Unequally Yoked</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Being unequally yoked refers to a believer entering into binding partnership with an unbeliever, particularly in marriage.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">The command (2 Corinthians 6:14):</strong> &quot;Do not be unequally yoked with unbelievers.&quot;</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Key truths:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The command is given to believers, not unbelievers</li>\n<li>&quot;He&#39;s a good man&quot; isn&#39;t enough — an unbeliever is spiritually dead (Ephesians 2:1-3)</li>\n<li>The husband God wants leads in love, sacrifices for his bride, sanctifies through the Word</li>\n<li>An unbeliever cannot do this</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">See <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=unequally-yoked</a> for detailed framework.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"concepts\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Concepts</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=courtship</a> — Intentional, marriage-oriented pursuit governed by God&#39;s Word</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=household-rhythms</a> — Daily, weekly, and habitual patterns that structure family life</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=biblical-manhood</a> — Defined by faithfulness, courage, and commitment</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=unequally-yoked</a> — Warning against believer-unbeliever romantic entanglement</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"connections\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Connections</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=rezy-laxa</a> — Spouse</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"sources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Sources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=a-field-guide-to-being-a-faithful-man</a> — Boaz&#39;s committed courtship as model</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=where-have-the-men-gone</a> — men fumbling in approach; practical advice to both</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=beware-of-the-zone-of-vulnerability</a> — warning to women about emotion-led attachment</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=life-in-between</a> — the young professional context: courtship as hard, worthy work</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=the-rhythm-of-the-household</a> — daily, weekly, and habitual patterns that structure family life</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=courted-by-a-good-zombie</a> — warning against being courted by an unbeliever</li>\n</ul>\n",
