      "slug": "be-resolved-in-an-age-of-unbelief",
      "title": "Be Resolved in an Age of Unbelief",
      "type": "resource",
      "tags": [
        "discipleship",
        "sanctification",
        "secularism",
        "new-year",
        "romans-12"
      ],
      "created": "Sat Apr 11 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "updated": "Sat Apr 11 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "faith",
      "excerpt": "Author: titus-jr-laxa\nPublished: 2025-01-06\nSource: tituslaxajr.substack.com A New Year exhortation drawn from Romans 12:1-3. We live in an age of unbelief manifested two ways — suppression and hiding of truth — and the...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"be-resolved-in-an-age-of-unbelief\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Be Resolved in an Age of Unbelief</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Author:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a>\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2025-01-06\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> tituslaxajr.substack.com</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">A New Year exhortation drawn from Romans 12:1-3. We live in an age of unbelief manifested two ways — suppression and hiding of truth — and the Christian must be resolved to resist it.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"key-points\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Points</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">The age of unbelief takes two forms:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>Suppression</em> — knowing God exists but refusing to acknowledge Him; leads to ingratitude, idolatry, immorality (Romans 1)</li>\n<li><em>Hiding</em> — doing the same sins secretly; the hypocrite&#39;s form of unbelief</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Evidence: broken marriages, iPhone-addicted families, young adults marching in Pride while attending church Sunday morning without guilt.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Three resolutions (Romans 12:1-3):</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">1. Be resolved to live.</strong> Spiritual life means living <em>for</em> God — presenting your body as a living sacrifice. Claims to be alive in Christ must be backed by fruit.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">2. Be resolved to change.</strong> Non-conformity requires mind renewal. Stop asking what your influencer or Taylor Swift would do; ask what God&#39;s Word says. Renewing the mind means acquiring a new <em>pattern</em> to imitate.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">3. Be resolved to get help.</strong> Lone-wolf Christianity breeds hypocrisy. You need honest Christians who will tell you your blind spots. Quotes Douglas Wilson: relationships that avoid honesty to keep the peace are built on lies.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Three means:</strong> prayer, regular Bible reading, being <em>in</em> (not just <em>at</em>) a church.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"concepts-touched\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Concepts touched</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sanctification</a> — change through mind renewal</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=hypocrisy</a> — the &quot;hiding truth&quot; form of unbelief</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=scripture</a> — the primary tool of mind renewal</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"related-resources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Related resources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=much-ado-about-hypocrisy</a> — deeper treatment of the hypocrisy dynamic</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=to-the-word-to-the-word</a> — the case for consistent Bible reading</li>\n</ul>\n",
