      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "faith",
      "excerpt": "Author: titus-jr-laxa\nSource: raw/notes/Level Up.md (sermon notes) Sermon notes on Colossians 2:6-7. God brings His people through new and harder experiences — not to break them but to grow them to a new level of faith....",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"level-up\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Level Up</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Author:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a>\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> raw/notes/Level Up.md (sermon notes)</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Sermon notes on Colossians 2:6-7. God brings His people through new and harder experiences — not to break them but to grow them to a new level of faith.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"key-points\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Points</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Theme:</strong> God brings you to new experiences you have never had — new family, rising prices, congregational problems you&#39;ve never faced — because the faith required for this new season is stronger than before. The purpose is not to crush you but to level you up.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">The right response:</strong> When leveled up, instead of letting go, press in. Instead of pulling away, draw closer.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Basis:</strong> &quot;You have received Christ Jesus the Lord&quot; — this is the foundation that doesn&#39;t change even as circumstances change.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Three ways God levels up faith:</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">1. By leveling up service</strong> (<em>rooted and built up</em>).\nExpect responsibilities to increase and grow more weighty. This is God deepening your roots and building your character and consistency through service — like a plant strengthened not just by nutrition but also by trials.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">2. By leveling up holiness</strong> (<em>established in the faith</em>).\nAs temptations increase and people who used to be cooperative start walking out — this is not evidence of failure. This is the test that establishes you more deeply in Christ.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">3. By leveling up thanksgiving.</strong>\nMore abundance, more responsibility — the proper response to both is growing gratitude.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"concepts-touched\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Concepts touched</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=gratitude</a> — thanksgiving as the response to all circumstances</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sanctification</a> — growth through trials and increased responsibility</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=worship</a> — living in Colossians 2 manner: rooted, built up, abounding in thanksgiving</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"related-resources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Related resources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=when-we-thank-god-for-all-things</a> — the thanksgiving theme expanded</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=bitter-tears-before-his-throne</a> — the harder complement: honest suffering before growth</li>\n</ul>\n",
