      "excerpt": "Author: titus-jr-laxa\nSource: https://tituslaxajr.com/\nPublished: N/A (Portfolio) Titus Jr Laxa's design portfolio showcasing work across web design, graphic design, and photography. The portfolio demonstrates a...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"titus-jr-laxa-visual-design-problem-solver\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Titus Jr Laxa | Visual Design Problem Solver</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Author:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a>\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">https://tituslaxajr.com/</a>\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> N/A (Portfolio)</p>\n<h1 id=\"summary\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Summary</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Titus Jr Laxa&#39;s design portfolio showcasing work across web design, graphic design, and photography. The portfolio demonstrates a commitment to solving real-world problems through clean layouts, clear messaging, and consistent execution. Titus Jr integrates theology and design thinking to craft solutions that are true, good, and beautiful.</p>\n<h1 id=\"work-categories\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Work Categories</h1>\n<h1 id=\"web-design\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Web Design</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Nonprofit Website | Kapatid Ministry</strong> — Ministry web presence</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Seminary Website | BBSI</strong> — Baptist Bible Seminary Institute</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Personal Blog | Merrel Ya</strong> — Blog design for wife Merrel</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Real Estate Website | MRA Realty</strong> — Real estate platform</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"graphic-design\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Graphic Design</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Missions Month | KLBC</strong> — Church missions materials</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">70th Anniversary | KLBC</strong> — Anniversary celebration design</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Worship with Sidney Mohede | KLBC</strong> — Event design</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Annual Report | Kapatid Ministry</strong> — Ministry annual report</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"photography\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Photography</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Street Photography | City of San Fernando, Pampanga</strong></li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Composition and Lighting</strong></li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Human Interest and Portrait Photography</strong></li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Travel Photography | Cambodia and Thailand</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"skills-amp-tools\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Skills &amp; Tools</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Design:</strong> Figma, Adobe XD, Sketch, UI/UX Design\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Adobe Suite:</strong> Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign, After Effects\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Photography:</strong> Photography, Lightroom\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Creative:</strong> Web Design, Branding</p>\n<h1 id=\"philosophy\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Philosophy</h1>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;I&#39;m looking to see how my theology impacts my design work. I hope to collaborate with those who want designs that are visually true, good, and beautiful that solves problems.&quot;</blockquote>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">The portfolio reflects multiple roles: husband to Rezy, Pastor in a Baptist Church, CEO of a nonprofit working with churches among marginalized communities in the Philippines, and Multimedia Arts Instructor.</p>\n<h1 id=\"related-pages\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Related Pages</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — biography and writings</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=work</a> — professional life; craft, design, career</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=design-thinking</a> — design as a lens, not a phase</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=stewardtrack</a> — church management SaaS project</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=shepherds-shelf</a> — personal library tracker project</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"quote\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Quote</h1>\n<blockquote class=\"pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary-container italic text-xl font-headline text-on-primary-container py-2 my-12\">&quot;I take seriously Jesus&#39; command to let my yes be yes, and no, no. So, this means that when I say yes to you, I will do it.&quot;</blockquote>\n",
