      "sources": 1,
      "domain": "faith",
      "excerpt": "Author: titus-jr-laxa\nPublished: 2025-01-12\nSource: tituslaxajr.substack.com A January exhortation to read the Bible this year — even if you've failed before. Drawn from Psalm 19:7-8, three kinds of people who need the...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"to-the-word-to-the-word\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">To The Word, To the Word</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Author:</strong> <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a>\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Published:</strong> 2025-01-12\n<strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Source:</strong> tituslaxajr.substack.com</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">A January exhortation to read the Bible this year — even if you&#39;ve failed before. Drawn from Psalm 19:7-8, three kinds of people who need the Word and what God will do for each through it.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"key-points\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Points</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Why people skip Bible reading plans:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Boredom — stuck at Genesis-to-Leviticus every year</li>\n<li>Busyness — work, parenting, life demands have increased</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Three audiences and three purposes (Psalm 19:7-8):</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">1. The dying soul → The Word revives.</strong>\nGod&#39;s law is perfect — without blemish — and therefore life-giving. Even the greatest and darkest sinner stands no chance against the Word&#39;s power to revive. Augustine&#39;s testimony: stuck in sexual immorality, he heard children&#39;s voices saying <em>&quot;tolle lege, tolle lege&quot;</em> (take up and read). He opened Romans 13, read about putting on Christ, and felt the burden of sin lift.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">2. The immature mind → The Word matures.</strong>\nImmaturity means being enslaved to feelings — making decisions by emotion, obeying God only when you feel like it. The Word makes wise the simple. Historical note: William Tyndale translated the Bible in defiance of church authorities so that the &quot;plow boy&quot; could know Scripture better than the clergy.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">3. The anxious heart → The Word rejoices.</strong>\nCharles Spurgeon: &quot;The worst forms of depression are cured when Holy Scripture is believed.&quot; Spurgeon himself suffered severe depression after a crowd-panic tragedy early in his ministry. He did not run from the Word — he ran toward it.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Closing:</strong> Don&#39;t read the Bible for Instagram performance (&quot;devotions with a matcha latte&quot;). Read it because your soul is dying, your mind is immature, or your heart is anxious.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"concepts-touched\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Concepts touched</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=scripture</a> — the central concept</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=sanctification</a> — transformation through the Word</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=lament</a> — the Word as cure for depression and anxiety</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"people-mentioned\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">People mentioned</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=augustine</a> — testimony of conversion through Scripture</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=william-tyndale</a> — fought for universal access to the Bible</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=charles-spurgeon</a> — depression and the Word</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"related-resources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Related resources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=growing-in-wisdom-a-guide-for-young-men</a> — Bible + books as the path to wisdom</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=be-resolved-in-an-age-of-unbelief</a> — mind renewal through the Word</li>\n</ul>\n",
