      "domain": "culture",
      "excerpt": "Notes from Titus Jr and Rezy's wedding preparation. --- Who must be present:\n- Rezy\n- Jr (Titus)\n- Parents\n- Kapatids (if available) When:\n- March (if possible) --- 1. Procession\n2...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"wedding-planning\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Wedding Planning</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Notes from Titus Jr and Rezy&#39;s wedding preparation.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"non-negotiables\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Non-Negotiables</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Who must be present:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Rezy</li>\n<li>Jr (Titus)</li>\n<li>Parents</li>\n<li>Kapatids (if available)</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">When:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>March (if possible)</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"programme\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Programme</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Procession</li>\n<li>Parents paalam</li>\n<li>Message</li>\n<li>Vows</li>\n<li>Ring</li>\n<li>Worship song</li>\n<li>Announcement</li>\n<li>Kiss the bride :)</li>\n<li>Recession / Picture</li>\n</ol>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"gifts\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Gifts</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">From Christmas 2022 notes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ptr. Hyman and Ate Amor</li>\n<li>Noel</li>\n<li>Ptr. Lloyd and Family</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"prayer-concerns\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Prayer Concerns</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Documented prayer items:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>God&#39;s provision</li>\n<li>Unity of families</li>\n<li>Clear Gospel witness</li>\n<li>Weather and logistics</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"needs-checklist\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Needs Checklist</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> Venue finalization</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> Programme details</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> Officiant</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> Guest list</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> Invitations</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> Catering</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> Attire</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> Music/worship</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> Documentation</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"see-also\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">See Also</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=rezy-laxa</a> — Spouse</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=relationships</a> — Marriage area</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=courtship</a> — Courtship framework</li>\n</ul>\n",
