      "created": "Sat Apr 11 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "updated": "Sat Apr 11 2026 08:00:00 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)",
      "sources": 3,
      "domain": "culture",
      "excerpt": "The domain of cultural engagement — analyzing media, social trends, and moral shifts through a Christian lens. Includes critique of destructive cultural forces and the formation of imagination. --- - shame — the...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"culture\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Culture</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">The domain of cultural engagement — analyzing media, social trends, and moral shifts through a Christian lens. Includes critique of destructive cultural forces and the formation of imagination.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"concepts\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Concepts</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=shame</a> — the protective moral signal being systematically dismantled in contemporary culture</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=storytelling</a> — the double-edged power of narrative: formative for good, weaponizable for harm</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=imagination</a> — the faculty narrative acts upon; imagination precedes desire</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=hypocrisy</a> — the dominant mode of unbelief in cultural Christianity: hiding rather than suppressing</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ai-and-faith</a> — AI as a cultural force requiring Christian discernment</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"people\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">People</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=michael-foster</a> — pastor engaging cultural trends around sexuality and family</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"resources\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Resources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=normalization-of-female-sexual-degeneracy</a> — BookTok, erotic fiction, the removal of shame from female sexual immorality</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=be-resolved-in-an-age-of-unbelief</a> — the age of unbelief: suppression and hiding; broken families, iPhone-addicted households, nominal Christianity</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ai-and-the-christian-life</a> — AI as pervasive cultural technology requiring a Christian framework</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"themes-emerging\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Themes emerging</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Storytelling is not neutral.</strong> The same mechanism that makes biblical narrative and family stories formative also makes erotic fiction dangerous.</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Asymmetric accountability.</strong> Male sexual sin is broadly condemned; female sexual sin is reframed as empowerment. This asymmetry is a cultural project.</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=imagination</a> precedes desire.</strong> &quot;What shapes imagination will, sooner or later, shape desire, and desire does not stay contained.&quot; (Foster)</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">The age of unbelief takes two forms.</strong> Open rebellion (suppression) and secret hypocrisy (hiding). Both end at the same waterfall.</li>\n<li><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">AI is the newest cultural tool with the oldest temptations.</strong> Idol potential, abdication of responsibility, and the displacement of human judgment.</li>\n</ul>\n",
