      "excerpt": "A Philippine-based ministry organization involved in church planting, children's ministry, and diaspora missions support. --- Bank Information:\n- Metrobank, Gen. Luis, Novaliches, Quezon City\n- Account Number:...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"kapatid-ministry-inc-kmi\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Kapatid Ministry Inc. (KMI)</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">A Philippine-based ministry organization involved in church planting, children&#39;s ministry, and diaspora missions support.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"key-details\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Key Details</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Bank Information:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Metrobank, Gen. Luis, Novaliches, Quezon City</li>\n<li>Account Number: 366-3-36621861-1</li>\n<li>Swift Code: MBTCPHMM</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\"><strong class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">Related Bank Account:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>BDO: 001250070390 (Elizabeth David Laxa - KMI)</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"leadership-and-meetings\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Leadership and Meetings</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">November 7, 2014 meeting attendees:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Elizabeth D. Laxa</li>\n<li>Chicky Decolongon</li>\n<li>Titus Laxa Jr</li>\n<li>Titus Laxa (Sr.?)</li>\n<li>Bobby Teraytay</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"programs\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Programs</h1>\n<h1 id=\"child-sponsorship-program\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Child Sponsorship Program</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Partnership with international supporters</li>\n<li>Thank you cards created for sponsors</li>\n<li>Brochures for promotional use</li>\n<li>Sis. Doreen as contact point</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"bread-distribution\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Bread Distribution</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Ptr. Bob coordinates delivery</li>\n<li>Extra bread distributed to LCBC and partner churches</li>\n<li>Pastors in need contacted for receiving</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"church-planting-support\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Church Planting Support</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>PBC (Pasay Baptist Church) mission trips</li>\n<li>Partner churches: LCBC, KLBC, FCCC, IBC</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"projects\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Projects</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Website development</li>\n<li>Database system design</li>\n<li>PCMN (Philippine Council of Mission agencies?) reporting</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"church-partners\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Church Partners</h1>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Church</th>\n<th>Location</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>LCBC (Llano Christian Baptist Church)</td>\n<td>Novaliches, Quezon City</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>KLBC</td>\n<td>Karuhatan</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>FCCC</td>\n<td>Filipino Christian Community Church</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>IBC</td>\n<td>International Baptist Church</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>PBC</td>\n<td>Pasay</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"diaspora-connection\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Diaspora Connection</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Ministry extends to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Singapore (through Rezy and Ptr. Lloyd)</li>\n<li>Malaysia</li>\n<li>Filipino OFW communities globally</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">See <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=tentmaking</a> for marketplace missions philosophy.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"see-also\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">See Also</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a> — Ministry involvement</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=rezy-laxa</a> — Singapore connection</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ministry</a> — Ministry area page</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=google-keep-archive</a> — Source material</li>\n</ul>\n",
