      "excerpt": "Designer and product leader. Active on X (Twitter) at @eeismann. Background includes roles as GM of Airbnb's Guest team (responsible for 97% of booking revenue) and design work at Slack...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"eeismann\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">@eeismann</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Designer and product leader. Active on X (Twitter) at @eeismann. Background includes roles as GM of Airbnb&#39;s Guest team (responsible for 97% of booking revenue) and design work at Slack. Writes on the future of design, AI&#39;s impact on product teams, and what craft means when production is commoditized.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"appearances-in-wiki\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Appearances in wiki</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=the-design-paradox</a> — the paradox of flat design jobs alongside increasing need for design thinking; design as a lens, not a phase</li>\n</ul>\n",
