      "excerpt": "A personal library tracker with AI-generated course creation built in. --- Track books read and owned, then use AI to turn that reading into structured learning paths or courses — especially useful for self-directed...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"shepherd-39-s-shelf\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Shepherd&#39;s Shelf</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">A personal library tracker with AI-generated course creation built in.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"goal\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Goal</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Track books read and owned, then use AI to turn that reading into structured learning paths or courses — especially useful for self-directed theological and pastoral study.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"status\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Status</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Active. In development.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"notes\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Notes</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Connects Titus Jr&#39;s self-directed doctoral-level study in Reformed Christian history with his interest in education and AI tools</li>\n<li>Reflects the same instinct as his wiki: turn raw reading into organized, usable knowledge</li>\n<li>Potential audience: pastors, Christian educators, independent scholars</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"links\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Links</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Area: <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=education</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=faith</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=work</a></li>\n<li>People: <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
