      "domain": "ministry",
      "excerpt": "Church management SaaS built specifically for Filipino ministries. --- Provide a low-friction, locally relevant digital tool for church administration — membership, giving records, attendance, and ministry coordination...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"stewardtrack\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">StewardTrack</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Church management SaaS built specifically for Filipino ministries.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"goal\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Goal</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Provide a low-friction, locally relevant digital tool for church administration — membership, giving records, attendance, and ministry coordination — designed with Filipino church culture in mind.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"status\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Status</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Active. In development.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"notes\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Notes</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Sits at Titus Jr&#39;s intersection of ministry and tech</li>\n<li>Audience: local churches in the Philippines</li>\n<li>Part of a broader pattern of building tools for underserved Christian communities</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"links\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Links</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Area: <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ministry</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=work</a></li>\n<li>People: <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=titus-jr-laxa</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
