      "excerpt": "Pastoral prayer concerns documented in ministry notes (sourced from google-keep-archive, 2013–2025). Consolidated from individual notes for ongoing intercession. --- - Revival in serving Jesus\n- Resolution to current...",
      "htmlContent": "<h1 id=\"prayer-list\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Prayer List</h1>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant\">Pastoral prayer concerns documented in ministry notes (sourced from <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=google-keep-archive</a>, 2013–2025). Consolidated from individual notes for ongoing intercession.</p>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"active-prayer-concerns\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Active Prayer Concerns</h1>\n<h1 id=\"andrea-belarmino\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Andrea Belarmino</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Revival in serving Jesus</li>\n<li>Resolution to current trouble; readiness to face challenge and consequence</li>\n<li>God&#39;s grace and mercy</li>\n<li>Provision to resolve challenges</li>\n<li>Strength and wisdom in the workplace</li>\n<li>Intimacy with God; return to first love</li>\n<li>Restoration of friendship and fellowship</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"altheo\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Altheo</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Flee temptation; grow spiritually</li>\n<li>Focus and faithfulness in Bagumbong ministry</li>\n<li>Sunday School teaching; equipping volunteers</li>\n<li>Wisdom in work decisions; guard against compromise</li>\n<li>Personal plans: future home, business</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"jamie\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Jamie</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Relationship and intimacy with God</li>\n<li>Time and priorities management</li>\n<li>Wisdom to resolve school challenges</li>\n<li>Favor and skill growth as a teacher</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"ella\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Ella</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete healing</li>\n<li>Financial provision for medications and hospital bills</li>\n<li>Comfort for family</li>\n<li>Salvation for family</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"angelo\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Angelo</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Work opportunity</li>\n<li>Deepening relationship with God</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"annielyn\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">Annielyn</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Suitable work close to God&#39;s purpose</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"my-12 border-0 border-t border-outline-variant/20\">\n<h1 id=\"see-also\" class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline text-on-surface mt-16 mb-6\">See Also</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=ministry</a> — Pastoral life area</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-primary transition-all\">entry.html?slug=google-keep-archive</a> — Source material</li>\n</ul>\n",
